:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-game-970-x-615px.jpg 970w, https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-game-970-x-615px-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-game-970-x-615px-768x487.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Double trouble! this fun memory game also makes a great set of cards for playing Snap.<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to Make<\/strong>:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Glue the pages to cardboard or a cereal box<\/li><li>Cut out each square piece (there are 54 in total &#8211; 27 pairs)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>To Play<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Lay all the pieces image facing down on a flat surface.<\/li><li>Take turns flipping over two cards at a time. If the cards have the the same picture, then they are yours and you get another turn. If they don\u2019t match, turn them back over (but remember where they are). Now it\u2019s the next player\u2019s turn.<\/li><li>Continue taking turns until all the cards have been matched. The person with the most pairs is the winner!<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Changing difficulty<\/strong>: for an easier game, play the game with less pairs on the board i.e. only place down eight pairs. Slowly increase the number of pairs in the game to increase the challenge. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>More fun! <\/strong>You can also use the cards for a game of Bluey Snap.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Memory-game.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download the game template<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Make the box to store your cards<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"970\" height=\"615\" src=\"https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-Box-Hero-Image-970x615px.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-Box-Hero-Image-970x615px.jpg 970w, https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-Box-Hero-Image-970x615px-300x190.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Craft-Memory-Box-Hero-Image-970x615px-768x487.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 970px) 100vw, 970px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>Fold &amp; Glue!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Ask a grown-up to help you cut around the dotted lines <\/li><li>Fold and glue<\/li><li>Use this box to keep your Bluey Memory Game tidy and safe. <\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/Bluey-Memory-game-box.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download the box template<\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-bbc-share-buttons social-buttons-holder\" aria-label=\"Collection of buttons to share on social media channels\"><div class=\"share-buttons\"><span>Share: <\/span><a class=\"icon__social icon__social--facebook__share\" href=\"https:\/\/facebook.com\/sharer\/sharer.php?u=https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/make\/bluey-memory-game\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Share on Facebook\">Share on Facebook<\/a><a class=\"icon__social icon__social--twitter__share\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet\/?text=Bluey Memory Game&amp;url=https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/make\/bluey-memory-game\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Share on Twitter\">Share on Twitter<\/a><a class=\"icon__social icon__social--copy-link\" href=\"https:\/\/www.bluey.tv\/make\/bluey-memory-game\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-label=\"Copy URL\">Copy URL<\/a><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1383,"template":"","meta":{"gbl_sidebar_theme_meta_field":["default-theme"]},"download-types":[11],"